headline: Telecom Operators Turn to Real-Time Analytics for Enhanced Network Performance and Customer Satisfaction
summary: Growth in the Big Data Analytics in Telecom Market is driven by telecom operators' need for real-time analytics to enhance network efficiency and customer experience. The European Commission’s Digital Decade initiative further propels demand for advanced analytics. Dominated by the solutions segment, the market leverages data management tools and cloud-based platforms. Key players like AWS and IBM focus on AI and machine learning for predictive insights.
